{"tid":1185530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國向東南亞四國出售34台無人機　分析料為遏制中國","createTime":"2019-06-04T10:13:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T12:13:10.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a43fcc0ba55f9368d314964631a5282b9ab0aff4","tid":1185530,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:13:04.000Z","msg":"美國向東南亞四國出售34台無人機　分析料為遏制中國 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20190604/s00005/1559622398941/%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e5%90%91%e6%9d%b1%e5%8d%97%e4%ba%9e%e5%9b%9b%e5%9c%8b%e5%87%ba%e5%94%ae34%e5%8f%b0%e7%84%a1%e4%ba%ba%e6%a9%9f-%e5%88%86%e6%9e%90%e6%96%99%e7%82%ba%e9%81%8f%e5%88%b6%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20190604%2Fs00005%2F1559622398941%2F%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%2590%2591%25e6%259d%25b1%25e5%258d%2597%25e4%25ba%259e%25e5%259b%259b%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%2594%25ae34%25e5%258f%25b0%25e7%2584%25a1%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25a9%259f-%25e5%2588%2586%25e6%259e%2590%25e6%2596%2599%25e7%2582%25ba%25e9%2581%258f%25e5%2588%25b6%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=51c847bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20190604%2Fs00005%2F1559622398941%2F%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%2590%2591%25e6%259d%25b1%25e5%258d%2597%25e4%25ba%259e%25e5%259b%259b%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%2594%25ae34%25e5%258f%25b0%25e7%2584%25a1%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25a9%259f-%25e5%2588%2586%25e6%259e%2590%25e6%2596%2599%25e7%2582%25ba%25e9%2581%258f%25e5%2588%25b6%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b&h=51676a00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20190604/s00005/1559622398941/%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e5%90%91%e6%9d%b1%e5%8d%97%e4%ba%9e%e5%9b%9b%e5%9c%8b%e5%87%ba%e5%94%ae34%e5%8f%b0%e7%84%a1%e4%ba%ba%e6%a9%9f-%e5%88%86%e6%9e%90%e6%96%99%e7%82%ba%e9%81%8f%e5%88%b6%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國防部宣布，將向四個東南亞國家，出售總共34台由波音公司製造的無武裝版無人機「掃描鷹」（Scan Eagle），總金額為4700萬美元（約3.68億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n這34台無人機將分別售往馬來西亞、印尼、菲律賓和越南4個國家，其中馬來西亞將購入12架，印尼和菲律賓均分別購入8架，其餘6架則由越南所購。<br />\n<br />\n國防部稱，這項合同除無人機外，還包括備用及修復零件、支援設備、工具、培訓等技術服務，預料會在2022年3月前完成軍售。<br />\n<br />\n路透社分析，這四個國家購入無人機，將有助他們提升蒐集情報能力，有助遏制中國在區內活動。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社）"},{"pid":"261c82e6d118e8a53231d4a2b70edd81f086b033","tid":1185530,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:26:32.000Z","msg":"無人機 易唔易比人 逆向工程？"},{"pid":"a29f3f6165f8231cf3c5be8d0b13556167fdfde6","tid":1185530,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"261c82e6d118e8a53231d4a2b70edd81f086b033","tid":1185530,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T10:26:32.000Z","msg":"無人機 易唔易比人 逆向工程？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T12:13:10.000Z","msg":"DIJ自主研發"}]}